The Contractor will be utilizing various lane closures from the Yadkin RIver Bridge (MM183) to just west of NC801 (Exit 180) in each direction of I-40. These closures will be nightly from 7:00PM - 7:00AM on I-40 Westbound and from 6:00PM - 5:00AM on I-40 Eastbound. Crews will utilize these closures for asphalt milling and paving operations. This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
